# Axis 3 — deep proper tail calls (intra-lane)

Deep self-tail-recursion at depth 2,000,000 with no unbounded managed/native
stack growth. This is the intra-lane (single portable-VM) form of the spec's
"mixed-language proper tail calls" conformance (§9). The cross-language form
(Scala↔ScalaScript N-function cycles at depth ≥1,000,000) belongs to the host
profiles and is tracked as pending until the host value/call bridge lands.

```scalascript
def loop(n: Int, acc: Int): Int =
  if n == 0 then acc else loop(n - 1, acc + 1)
println(loop(2000000, 0))
```
